_on_going_public_at":"2016-12-16T19:55:50.385Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"mrb_time_initialize sets the data pointer to NULL before parsing function arguments. Parsing function arguments can call out to ruby code to call methods to do type coercion. If the type coercion method tries to access the time object it will dereference a NULL pointer.\n\nThe following snippet results in a native crash under mruby-engine:\n```\n$x = Time.new\nclass Tmp\n    def to_i\n        $x.mday\n    end\nend\n$x.initialize Tmp.new\n```\n\nAttached is a patch to mruby to fix this issue.","weakness":{"id":48,"name":"Uncontrolled Resource Consumption"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":134831,"file_name":"patch4.diff","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/134/831/68b941bcff7e923494ccbe34e844806d3ef81bee/patch4.diff?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22patch4.diff%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27patch4.diff\u0026response-content-type=text%2Fx-diff\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQSRJDU26H%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T103949Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQC1TD5Mu1YWzBaT9JoBxUe%2BZvJlNmMfiK5NQSePe5LR4wIhAP7GzQSkc0E%2BOE06RN7rTmjDOZjX8S%2BKkgi4TCsjZ6WSKroFCPL%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzR%2BCydA3o5o26nnyUqjgUJry%2BOWfdkmFQTlXuMf1FaD1yHmJsoxKPcGvdtcrX6QiHnO37kETMfV1WL9s9Tjvo7Cf%2FisIA%2BS%2FBbkn2hXXJs6H2KAnQMWCt6RdlxosXxoo4Ec8ECnUflKLK2%2B%2B7iVOrhJevmek3IV21BhmCY8oREqsF4%2F2EuIvZcsurPzfItQ%2BNuSoJpxKmDroe%2FvLO%2FDfzYKuPJO9f7ly9dNx9x%2BHY88g43edQaPehj29uv8JkmkcrWEMnJPV%2FxxEqnEt9LyQ%2BsbL4z98adMwksuYpdGxRaUnqaxsWNYJ4oZnV8S73WmSUHsOP5F4AEHT02HnHMw0BeiAfuGFYshE%2FcsiMQ5PEfwRizq8iQJVO%2FJfxJz4CgpeUuVmWqhqu9pu9%2F9i5ZclND7lOcuOGerfQnwisxuzIL4